      <p class="text-xl text-white mb-8 opacity-90">
        Join thousands of happy creators who've discovered the joy of beautiful PDF editing!
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/signup" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-yellow-400 hover:bg-yellow-500 text-purple-800 font-bold rounded-full transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg text-lg">
          🌟 Start Your Free Journey
